metadata.description:
Block 137700130 
----------------
0VERGLOW is a limited collection of street film photography captured at night and further stylized to construct Nonce City: an underground metropolis hidden in the depths of the metaverse. 

The city of Nonce is a dystopian cyberpunk existence set in the year 2087. Each photograph depicts a precise moment on ETH block time throughout the city.
